  "title": "Production Technician (Chemical) (West Side)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Role Overview:</strong></h3>\n<p>Responsible for operating and maintaining chemical processing and support equipment, ensuring smooth production workflows, safety compliance, and quality control in a pilot-scale manufacturing environment.</p>\n<h3><strong>Core Duties:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensuring all machinery and tools are clean before starting a batch to prevent contamination.</li>\n  <li>Following instructions on the Production Order to select the correct components, equipment, and production cycle.</li>\n  <li>Performing any necessary adjustments or dilutions as directed by the lab.</li>\n  <li>Picking materials from the warehouse and packing finished products as specified.</li>\n  <li>Assisting in resolving any operational issues.</li>\n  <li>Keeping your work area clean and ensuring proper use of PPE</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Qualifications &amp; Skills:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manufacturing/Production experience in Semicon/Chemical industry</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you are interested in the position , kindly send your CVs in to jasper.soh(@)randstad.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please include your availability, expected salary and reason for leaving your current job</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA: 94C3609 / Reg: R25154228</p>",
